						<p>On a pillar set up before the Madanagōpālasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva, 1548 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1470, Kīlaka, Mārgaśira śu. 11, Thursday</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1548 A.D., November 11.</hi> The weekday, however, was <hi rend="bold">Sunday.</hi></p>						

